1
00:00:11,353 --> 00:00:12,479
What's going on?

2
00:00:12,479 --> 00:00:15,381
You don't usually ask me to hang out.

3
00:00:15,381 --> 00:00:18,342
I have something to ask you.

4
00:00:18,342 --> 00:00:21,437
Did something happen to Kim Yeon Du today?

5
00:00:21,437 --> 00:00:23,431
Kim Yeon Du?

6
00:00:25,217 --> 00:00:28,403
Is that why you wanted to see me?

7
00:00:29,138 --> 00:00:32,398
Why else would I ask you to hang out?

8
00:00:33,458 --> 00:00:36,420
If it's about her, ask her yourself.

9
00:00:36,420 --> 00:00:38,972
I don't have anything to say.

10
00:00:39,965 --> 00:00:41,799
What do you mean?

11
00:00:41,799 --> 00:00:43,668
Did you do something to her?

12
00:00:43,668 --> 00:00:46,146
Why does everyone assume I would do something to her?

13
00:00:46,146 --> 00:00:48,864
Do Ye Seok, Kim Yeon Du, and now even you.

14
00:00:48,864 --> 00:00:51,510
Why is everyone treating me like this?

15
00:00:56,006 --> 00:00:59,141
Can't you just take my side?

16
00:00:59,141 --> 00:01:00,969
What?

17
00:01:00,969 --> 00:01:03,063
Can't you console me?

18
00:01:03,063 --> 00:01:04,382
What are you saying?

19
00:01:04,382 --> 00:01:06,457
I like you, Ji Hyeon Ho.

20
00:01:08,243 --> 00:01:10,519
I've come to like you.

21
00:01:18,628 --> 00:01:22,340
You know what you're saying is nonsense, right?

22
00:01:23,359 --> 00:01:25,427
Why is it nonsense?

23
00:01:25,427 --> 00:01:29,629
Do you think it doesn't make sense that I like you?

24
00:01:29,629 --> 00:01:31,875
Was this your intention from the beginning?

25
00:01:31,875 --> 00:01:34,910
Is this why you wanted to form an alliance or something?

26
00:01:34,910 --> 00:01:35,637
At that time—

27
00:01:35,662 --> 00:01:39,110
Let's stop it.

28
00:01:39,200 --> 00:01:42,600
The alliance is over as of today.

29
00:01:47,282 --> 00:01:49,400
Ji Hyeon Ho!

30
00:01:54,548 --> 00:01:59,390
[Best Mistake 3]

31
00:02:11,031 --> 00:02:14,442
Of course, I've come to see you. Have you eaten yet?

32
00:02:14,442 --> 00:02:15,843
You haven't, right? Then let's go have a meal with me.

33
00:02:15,843 --> 00:02:17,929
Um... Well...

34
00:02:17,929 --> 00:02:21,990
I have an assignment to do today.

35
00:02:21,990 --> 00:02:23,470
With Senior Dae Yeong.

36
00:02:23,474 --> 00:02:24,661
- I knew it.
- Yes.

37
00:02:24,661 --> 00:02:26,520
I knew it.

38
00:02:28,865 --> 00:02:30,892
They have the best garlic bread.

39
00:02:30,892 --> 00:02:33,436
- Have a bite.
- Okay.

40
00:02:39,168 --> 00:02:45,987
Having seen them together just for a day is so hard, and she had put up with this for years.

41
00:02:45,987 --> 00:02:47,875
Hey, Ju Ho!

42
00:02:50,387 --> 00:02:53,030
She doesn't fit into our group. She's different from us.

43
00:02:53,030 --> 00:02:55,808
You look so pathetic right now.

44
00:02:55,808 --> 00:03:00,027
It's not the right time for a relationship.

45
00:03:00,027 --> 00:03:01,722
Sorry?

46
00:03:01,722 --> 00:03:03,541
Seol.

47
00:03:04,901 --> 00:03:08,935
I am going to study abroad.

48
00:03:20,167 --> 00:03:22,777
Even though she dumped me, I wouldn't have anything to say.

49
00:03:24,688 --> 00:03:27,400
I was so unashamed.

50
00:03:44,483 --> 00:03:46,501
Seo Ju Ho!

51
00:03:47,836 --> 00:03:49,870
What's going on? What brings you here?

52
00:03:49,870 --> 00:03:51,889
Is everything okay?

53
00:03:53,575 --> 00:03:58,093
I just have something I want to tell you.

54
00:03:58,093 --> 00:03:59,897
Something to tell?

55
00:04:01,458 --> 00:04:03,326
Well...

56
00:04:07,814 --> 00:04:09,532
Sorry.

57
00:04:11,718 --> 00:04:13,311
What are you sorry for?

58
00:04:13,311 --> 00:04:15,129
For everything.

59
00:04:17,324 --> 00:04:19,425
I'm sorry for everything.

60
00:04:23,897 --> 00:04:26,849
I'm sorry I didn't see that you liked me.

61
00:04:27,484 --> 00:04:29,352
I'm sorry I took Yeon Du's side in front of you,

62
00:04:29,352 --> 00:04:32,204
and I misunderstood you were bullying her.

63
00:04:33,131 --> 00:04:35,541
I'm sorry I said hurtful things.

64
00:04:37,410 --> 00:04:39,520
I'm sorry I made you cry.

65
00:04:42,774 --> 00:04:44,209
What's with you?

66
00:04:44,209 --> 00:04:47,120
Why are you bringing up the past all of a sudden?

67
00:04:48,046 --> 00:04:52,939
I'm sorry that I made you feel lonely and confess your feeling to me first.

68
00:04:53,969 --> 00:04:56,337
And I didn't tell you I was going to study abroad sooner.

69
00:04:56,337 --> 00:04:58,281
I'm sorry I made you wait for me

70
00:04:58,281 --> 00:05:00,908
and came back without telling you.

71
00:05:02,519 --> 00:05:04,578
Most of all,

72
00:05:07,941 --> 00:05:12,742
I'm sorry that I'm only realizing these now.

73
00:05:20,287 --> 00:05:22,930
I'm sorry for everything, Seol.

74
00:05:25,042 --> 00:05:26,984
I'm sorry.

75
00:05:32,132 --> 00:05:34,342
Seo Ju Ho.

76
00:05:34,342 --> 00:05:37,171
When you told me to have an unrequited love for you,

77
00:05:37,171 --> 00:05:40,613
I thought you were playing hard to get.

78
00:05:40,613 --> 00:05:44,775
I thought you were trying to get the upper hand in the relationship or something.

79
00:05:44,775 --> 00:05:47,570
That's why I felt frustrated,

80
00:05:51,652 --> 00:05:53,878
but I don't feel that way anymore.

81
00:05:56,907 --> 00:05:58,350
Doing this for a few months,

82
00:05:58,350 --> 00:06:01,777
or even for a few years is okay with me.

83
00:06:03,330 --> 00:06:07,832
I'll have an unrequited love for you this time around, until you like me back again.

84
00:06:12,172 --> 00:06:16,483
I'll just stay by your side, liking you with all my heart.

85
00:06:19,388 --> 00:06:22,272
So come whenever you're ready.

86
00:06:22,272 --> 00:06:24,158
Seol,

87
00:06:29,315 --> 00:06:32,333
I'll be waiting here forever.

88
00:06:49,401 --> 00:06:51,802
Hey, you, Coach!

89
00:06:51,802 --> 00:06:53,980
Are you sure you want to win this?

90
00:06:53,980 --> 00:06:57,040
How could you take out Choi Seung Hyeon from the roster

91
00:06:57,040 --> 00:07:00,686
if you want to win?

92
00:07:01,454 --> 00:07:03,389
What kind of coach are you?

93
00:07:03,389 --> 00:07:05,808
You don't have an eye for good players, do you?

94
00:07:05,808 --> 00:07:08,627
Our ace, the promising player.

95
00:07:08,627 --> 00:07:09,519
Fiery bat.

96
00:07:09,519 --> 00:07:10,847
- An Yu Na?
- How could you

97
00:07:10,872 --> 00:07:13,882
remove Choi Seung Hyeon?

98
00:07:15,268 --> 00:07:17,780
Stop laughing and say something, please.

99
00:07:17,780 --> 00:07:20,650
[JA College News: JA College Baseball Advanced to Finals at the 56th National Collegiate Baseball Presidential Cup!]

100
00:07:24,260 --> 00:07:29,511
I'll watch how well you would do it without him.

101
00:07:30,141 --> 00:07:32,484
I hope you lose.

102
00:07:34,020 --> 00:07:35,021
No, that's not good.

103
00:07:35,021 --> 00:07:36,697
You scared me!

104
00:07:40,677 --> 00:07:43,212
Hey, Choi Seung Hyeon.

105
00:07:43,212 --> 00:07:48,806
Team score is as important as an individual player's score.

106
00:07:50,729 --> 00:07:52,163
Okay.

107
00:07:52,163 --> 00:07:54,948
What brought you here?

108
00:07:54,948 --> 00:07:56,992
Did you really come here

109
00:07:59,696 --> 00:08:02,806
to fight with the coach or something?

110
00:08:02,806 --> 00:08:04,991
No.

111
00:08:04,991 --> 00:08:06,819
Never.

112
00:08:07,654 --> 00:08:09,530
I wasn't going to.

113
00:08:14,286 --> 00:08:21,629
Actually... I was just bothered about what I did to you the last time

114
00:08:23,361 --> 00:08:27,204
and worried about you too. That's why.

115
00:08:39,539 --> 00:08:42,030
- By chance—
- By chance—

116
00:08:47,260 --> 00:08:48,911
You go, first.

117
00:08:48,911 --> 00:08:51,546
No, you go first.

118
00:08:51,546 --> 00:08:53,406
Okay.

119
00:08:55,410 --> 00:08:58,694
Do you have some time later?

120
00:08:59,439 --> 00:09:01,799
Later?

121
00:09:04,193 --> 00:09:09,178
If you're free, would you like to grab pizza with me?

122
00:09:11,226 --> 00:09:12,593
I mean,

123
00:09:12,593 --> 00:09:16,022
I heard there is this new pizza place that opened near school recently,

124
00:09:16,022 --> 00:09:18,098
and their pizza is the bomb.

125
00:09:20,235 --> 00:09:22,561
And it's huge, too.

126
00:09:22,561 --> 00:09:26,582
So I can't eat it all alone.

127
00:09:26,582 --> 00:09:29,567
That's why.

128
00:09:29,567 --> 00:09:31,345
Okay.

129
00:09:33,265 --> 00:09:35,390
Really?

130
00:09:35,390 --> 00:09:37,418
Let's go together.

131
00:09:40,580 --> 00:09:42,215
You're lying.

132
00:09:42,215 --> 00:09:45,308
No, I'm not.

133
00:09:45,308 --> 00:09:47,387
You are.

134
00:09:47,387 --> 00:09:50,156
I don't lie.

135
00:09:51,115 --> 00:09:53,592
You're right. You don't lie.

136
00:09:53,592 --> 00:09:55,227
Yes.

137
00:09:57,439 --> 00:09:58,489
Let's go.

138
00:09:58,489 --> 00:10:00,290
Okay.

139
00:10:02,185 --> 00:10:03,619
That's her, right?

140
00:10:03,619 --> 00:10:05,495
Isn't she that girl? The freshman, Kim Yeon Du?

141
00:10:05,495 --> 00:10:07,589
I think that's her.

142
00:10:08,233 --> 00:10:10,585
So she's going out with Do Ye Seok, right?

143
00:10:10,585 --> 00:10:11,611
Yes.

144
00:10:11,640 --> 00:10:14,812
She flirted with him like crazy and she's finally dating him.

145
00:10:16,374 --> 00:10:18,641
Hey, Do Ye Seok has a new girlfriend now.

146
00:10:18,641 --> 00:10:19,644
Check out, 'Everytime.'

147
00:10:19,644 --> 00:10:21,328
For real?

148
00:10:22,742 --> 00:10:26,209
Does Sophomore Do Ye Seok in Business Management has a girlfriend?

149
00:10:26,209 --> 00:10:29,095
It looked like he was really close with

150
00:10:29,095 --> 00:10:31,297
Kim Yeon Du on that post on 'Everytime.'

151
00:10:31,297 --> 00:10:34,760
Are they dating?

152
00:10:37,888 --> 00:10:39,922
- Hey, Yeon Du.
- Oh?

153
00:10:39,922 --> 00:10:41,974
Senior.

154
00:10:44,919 --> 00:10:48,064
I think people have got the wrong idea because of the post.

155
00:10:48,064 --> 00:10:52,983
I thought everything would be okay once the post was taken down.

156
00:10:53,845 --> 00:10:55,721
I was wrong.

157
00:10:57,307 --> 00:11:00,934
I'm sorry I've dragged you into this.

158
00:11:00,934 --> 00:11:03,453
But don't worry.

159
00:11:03,453 --> 00:11:04,922
I'll fix it.

160
00:11:04,922 --> 00:11:07,733
Once I write that it's not true on Everytime—

161
00:11:08,693 --> 00:11:12,327
I'm okay so you don't have to do that.

162
00:11:12,327 --> 00:11:14,398
Sorry?

163
00:11:14,398 --> 00:11:17,060
Don't write that.

164
00:11:17,060 --> 00:11:19,945
What do you mean?

165
00:11:19,945 --> 00:11:22,473
At this point, whatever you say,

166
00:11:22,473 --> 00:11:24,766
no one would believe you.

167
00:11:24,766 --> 00:11:27,703
People will say we're dating secretly or something,

168
00:11:27,703 --> 00:11:30,322
and it can make the rumor snowball.

169
00:11:32,050 --> 00:11:36,359
Also this is not your fault.

170
00:11:38,765 --> 00:11:43,759
It's the vice president who should be fixing it, not you.

171
00:11:43,759 --> 00:11:46,355
You're right, but still...

172
00:11:46,355 --> 00:11:49,349
People will forget it quickly after some time.

173
00:11:49,349 --> 00:11:51,752
Don't worry too much.

174
00:11:51,752 --> 00:11:55,171
Also whatever this is, don't you think

175
00:11:55,171 --> 00:11:58,133
two is better than one for now?

176
00:11:59,811 --> 00:12:03,128
Something like this might happen again and all.

177
00:12:03,957 --> 00:12:07,024
Okay, I got it.

178
00:12:25,896 --> 00:12:27,730
You stay.

179
00:12:29,132 --> 00:12:31,167
I'll leave.

180
00:12:37,365 --> 00:12:39,233
What are you doing?

181
00:12:40,643 --> 00:12:42,853
I'm sorry for accusing you last time.

182
00:12:42,853 --> 00:12:44,597
It's my bad.

183
00:12:44,622 --> 00:12:47,332
You don't have to avoid me.

184
00:12:48,168 --> 00:12:49,060
Okay.

185
00:12:49,060 --> 00:12:52,378
I'll accept your apology.

186
00:12:52,378 --> 00:12:55,349
Even though it doesn't feel like you mean it.

187
00:12:58,912 --> 00:13:05,571
A strange rumor is going around, that you and Kim Yeon Du are dating.

188
00:13:08,896 --> 00:13:10,840
They're so funny.

189
00:13:10,840 --> 00:13:13,775
All you did was just to take care of her as a senior,

190
00:13:14,735 --> 00:13:18,270
but they've misunderstood you, saying you two are dating.

191
00:13:18,270 --> 00:13:20,198
Am I right?

192
00:13:21,659 --> 00:13:23,511
They're not wrong.

193
00:13:24,896 --> 00:13:26,455
What?

194
00:13:26,455 --> 00:13:28,780
I like her.

195
00:13:30,777 --> 00:13:33,350
I thought you knew.

196
00:13:35,756 --> 00:13:37,341
Really?

197
00:13:37,341 --> 00:13:40,377
You must be happy now then.

198
00:13:40,377 --> 00:13:41,846
I didn't know

199
00:13:41,846 --> 00:13:45,541
that there would be someone who would benefit from this juvenile rumor.

200
00:13:48,019 --> 00:13:51,990
Juvenile rumors would die out quickly as you said.

201
00:13:51,990 --> 00:13:55,110
But if she can be safe for a bit...

202
00:13:55,113 --> 00:13:59,127
Well, I guess that can be a benefit.

203
00:14:15,730 --> 00:14:17,339
- You want to grab a bite?
- Yeah, how about the cafeteria?

204
00:14:17,339 --> 00:14:19,191
Cool.

205
00:14:27,100 --> 00:14:28,283
Hey. Hey.

206
00:14:28,283 --> 00:14:30,910
Did you hear Kim Yeon Du and Do Ye Seok are dating?

207
00:14:30,910 --> 00:14:32,797
Of course.

208
00:14:32,797 --> 00:14:34,791
It makes sense.

209
00:14:34,833 --> 00:14:37,709
Honestly, Yeon Du is pretty, cute, and innocent.

210
00:14:37,709 --> 00:14:39,446
She's every guy's type.

211
00:14:39,446 --> 00:14:40,647
You're right.

212
00:14:40,647 --> 00:14:44,307
Jin Se Hui is pretty, but she is a type of girl that you get sick of easily.

213
00:14:44,307 --> 00:14:48,144
I'm sure that's a part of the reason, why they broke up.

214
00:14:48,144 --> 00:14:49,388
Pathetic.

215
00:14:49,413 --> 00:14:52,707
Jin Se Hui gets to pass down her title, The Goddess of Business Management, to Kim Yeon Du now.

216
00:14:52,707 --> 00:14:53,476
Hey.

217
00:14:53,500 --> 00:14:56,900
Goddess? My butt. She only backstabbed her boyfriend.

218
00:14:56,944 --> 00:14:59,090
Do Ye Seok must be a better judge of character now.

219
00:14:59,090 --> 00:15:01,699
Kim Yeon Du doesn't look like a thief at least.

220
00:15:01,699 --> 00:15:04,511
He must've gotten better after he got backstabbed by Jin Se Hui.

221
00:15:05,596 --> 00:15:08,431
Hey! You know I can hear you, right?

222
00:15:08,431 --> 00:15:10,651
Just say it in front of me.

223
00:15:10,651 --> 00:15:11,527
Oops, sorry!

224
00:15:11,527 --> 00:15:12,862
Did you hear that?

225
00:15:12,862 --> 00:15:14,500
Oh, my! I didn't know you were there.

226
00:15:14,500 --> 00:15:16,680
You've such a little presence.

227
00:15:16,680 --> 00:15:19,401
Did I say anything that isn't true though?

228
00:15:19,401 --> 00:15:22,028
- Let's go.
- Okay.

229
00:16:10,903 --> 00:16:13,870
[Kim Yeon Du]

230
00:16:19,821 --> 00:16:22,623
Is it really okay to just leave the rumor alone?

231
00:16:22,623 --> 00:16:26,130
It's not like we're actually dating.

232
00:16:36,430 --> 00:16:38,560
[Anonymity: I've found it at the cafeteria.]
[Principles of Business]

233
00:16:38,560 --> 00:16:40,457
This is my book.

234
00:16:40,457 --> 00:16:42,226
I've found it in the cafeteria.

235
00:16:42,226 --> 00:16:46,771
If it belongs to you, go get it at B102 in the Business Management's building.

236
00:16:46,771 --> 00:16:49,416
Why was this at the cafeteria?

237
00:16:50,351 --> 00:16:52,953
Did it slip out of my bag?

238
00:16:55,982 --> 00:17:00,980
B102 in the Business Management building?

239
00:17:18,905 --> 00:17:22,275
Why is it underground of all floors? It's scary.

240
00:17:25,912 --> 00:17:28,064
Oh! There it is.

241
00:17:28,064 --> 00:17:30,930
I'm going to grab it quickly.

242
00:17:47,666 --> 00:17:51,370
[Darkroom]

243
00:18:22,819 --> 00:18:26,371
It's not fair for you to be like that while I was gone to pick up drinks.

244
00:18:27,991 --> 00:18:32,651
It's not fair for you to butt in on our date.

245
00:18:35,672 --> 00:18:36,766
What date?

246
00:18:36,766 --> 00:18:39,220
Don't say such a scary thing.

247
00:18:43,331 --> 00:18:47,065
Well, it's because I happened to have two gift vouchers

248
00:18:47,065 --> 00:18:48,986
and we just ended up watching a movie together.

249
00:18:48,986 --> 00:18:50,946
Why don't we go play a game together?

250
00:18:50,946 --> 00:18:53,048
It's on me.

251
00:18:53,925 --> 00:18:56,152
What game are you talking about Ah Hun?

252
00:18:56,152 --> 00:18:57,020
How about shopping then?

253
00:18:57,020 --> 00:18:59,187
You can shop with it, too.

254
00:18:59,187 --> 00:19:02,440
What should I do with you?

255
00:19:04,927 --> 00:19:06,228
Ah Hun.

256
00:19:06,228 --> 00:19:10,546
By the way, don't you have a tutoring lesson today?

257
00:19:11,192 --> 00:19:14,826
Right. What happened to your lesson?

258
00:19:15,680 --> 00:19:17,781
Did you skip it?

259
00:19:18,516 --> 00:19:20,126
What do you think of me?

260
00:19:20,126 --> 00:19:22,419
The lesson got canceled.

261
00:19:22,419 --> 00:19:24,390
Canceled?

262
00:19:24,390 --> 00:19:25,521
Why?

263
00:19:25,521 --> 00:19:26,666
I don't know.

264
00:19:26,691 --> 00:19:28,217
I couldn't get a hold of Yeon Du.

265
00:19:28,217 --> 00:19:30,644
So I just left after waiting for so long.

266
00:19:30,644 --> 00:19:31,887
What?

267
00:19:31,887 --> 00:19:34,522
You couldn't get a hold of Yeon Du?

268
00:19:36,117 --> 00:19:37,951
No way.

269
